aleigh or perhaps Crooke in North Tawton (both Devon), which are derived from this word."]},{"name":"Croston","meanings":["English (Lancashire): habitational name from a place in Lancashire named Croston, from Old Norse <i>kross</i> ‘cross’ or Old English <i>cros</i> + Old English <i>tūn</i> ‘farmstead, settlement’.","English: occasionally, a variant of   Croxton   or   Croson  ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Croxton was born about 1380, in England, United Kingdom. He married Elizabeth Leycester about 1405, in Lancashire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter."},"et":{"about 1380–":"umbes 1380–Surnud","1385–1416":"1385–1416","1405–Male":"1405–Surnud","1413–1487":"1413–1487","1380–Male":"1380–Surnud","1413":"1413","about 1380":"umbes 1380","about 1405":"umbes 1405","1487":"1487","1385":"1385","1380":"1380","1405":"1405","1416":"1416","Middlewich, Cheshire, England":"Middlewich, Cheshire, England","Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Croxton, Cheshire, England":"Croxton, Cheshire, England","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1380–":"noin 1380–Kuollut","1385–1416":"1385–1416","1405–Male":"1405–Kuollut","1413–1487":"1413–1487","1380–Male":"1380–Kuollut","1413":"1413","about 1380":"noin 1380","about 1405":"noin 1405","1487":"1487","1385":"1385","1380":"1380","1405":"1405","1416":"1416","Middlewich, Cheshire, England":"Middlewich, Cheshire, England","Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Croxton, Cheshire, England":"Croxton, Cheshire, England","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1380–":"environ 1380–Décédé","1385–1416":"1385–1416","1405–Male":"1405–Décédé","1413–1487":"1413–1487","1380–Male":"1380–Décédé","1413":"1413","about 1380":"environ 1380","about 1405":"environ 1405","1487":"1487","1385":"1385","1380":"1380","1405":"1405","1416":"1416","Middlewich, Cheshire, England":"Mid